{"tid":1285750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同林鄭對話？對你老母呀？","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:54:21.000Z","uid":122994,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c01c1bf78775b12b9496fd18181a39bb8d49e3cc","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:31:31.000Z","msg":"香港人醒下啦，林鄭掟個咩撚野「對話」出黎就咁多人想含？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除非係林鄭公開面對全港市民，唔係公唔公開都唔好接受呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 四大訴求全部都係是與非，一係承認一係唔承認，咩有得談判咩？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭一早知我地有五大訴求<br />\na. 撤回 = 一係撤一係唔撤<br />\nb. 暴動定義 = 一係撤一係唔撤<br />\nc. 特赦 = 一係特赦一係特赦<br />\nd. 獨立委員會 = 一係成立一係唔成立<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係傾加唔加關稅，加幾多關稅咁有得<span style=\"color: red;\">談判</span>呀！唔通你想同佢傾「幾時徹回」，「特赦幾多個」呀？<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，咁有咩撚野好對話呀？談心呀？聽下佢呢排有幾辛苦呀？四大訴求佢一係應承一係唔應承啦！對佢老母呀？<br />\n<br />\n2. 無人可以代表<br />\n<br />\n令次既運動無大台，無leader就係人都知。既然係咁，咁邊有人可以代表全港人同林鄭對話呀？<br />\n對完等分化呀？<br />\n<br />\n另外，既然代表唔到，咁對話黎就咩呀？你又應承唔到佢任何野，唔小心應承左又要比我地屌。咁對黎做咩？<br />\n<br />\n3. 傾雙普選？<br />\n<br />\n佢有誠意就自己重啟政改啦！另外同第二點一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">咩佢話到事咩</span>？你要傾雙著選既話就叫個話到事既人黎見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 阻礙其他運動<br />\n<br />\n14年既失敗大家都仲歷歷在目。學聯五子應承左同林奠傾，結果全世界都觀望同等佢地傾，最後升級又升唔到，其他所有運動一律搞唔起，總之就係中曬佢緩兵之計。<br />\n<br />\n我咁講佢任何一個人應承左對話，佢都會搞勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又set對話日期，又set對話地點咩咩柒柒咁！期間死黑警就會繼續大搜捕，而義士被捕既消息就會比咩撚野對話搶曬focus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.敬告左膠、民陣、泛民，槍口對外<br />\n<br />\n親愛既左膠，我知你地有鋪對話、溝通癮，覺得對話同溝通可以解決萬事。但sorry，依家擺明林奠只係想拖，只係行緊詭計咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果林奠真係有溝通既誠意同意向，佢一早就有<span style=\"color: red;\">行動</span>，例如四大訴求做左三樣先，釋出善意。依家佢咩撚野都無做，同五年前一樣得個講字咋，佢想傾？咪撚on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之大家槍口一致對外，咪撚理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b121fc35b6f2d7778f401bfe9fe7556417642c92","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e63e345e6866ebde1bf517d2ee0a1301cb12949","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"182540dc53e8bc9a3c60f5b77ef98be1f11686e8","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a827bcce004facc4fc5bbcaee8c9c7432fc5f59","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"記住歷史既教訓"},{"pid":"3c1d9d1694c74675b484fdb7db5749c33c35936b","tid":1285750,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/hJy832m.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJy832m.gif&h=43898d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廢老光頭跳舞幫推"},{"pid":"afd6a45347c2ae5c0c725409cae17908b6b74b9e","tid":1285750,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:33:31.000Z","msg":"五年前學聯含過，唔係依家又含返同一條撚呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1296420f323b4847bcbe15d4a8891de5049b2e54","tid":1285750,"uid":1